# [http://www.cems.uwe.ac.uk/xmlwiki/Music/mxl2arduino.xq?uri=http://www.hymnsandcarolsofchristmas.com/Hymns_and_Carols/XML/Good_King_Wenceslas2.xml Good King Wensceslas]
# [http://www.cems.uwe.ac.uk/xmlwiki/Music/mxl2arduinoForm.xq?uri=http://www.hymnsandcarolsofchristmas.com/Hymns_and_Carols/XML/Good_King_Wenceslas2.xml HTML Form interface]

